quran[7{c,v,t}:
34,1,hamd uss khuda ke liye hai jo asmano aur zameen ki har cheez ka maalik hai aur akhirat mein bhi isi ke liye hamd hai woh Dana aur bakhabar hai
34,2,"jo kuch zameen mein jata hai aur jo kuch uss se nikalta hai aur jo kuch aasman se utartaa hai aur jo kuch uss mein charhata hai, har cheez ko woh jaanta hai, woh Raheem aur ghafoor hai"
34,3,"munkareen kehte hain ke kya baat hai ke qayamat hum par nahi aa rahi hai! kaho, qasam hai mere aalam ul ghaibparvar-digaar ki, woh tum par aa kar rahay gi uss se zarra barabar koi cheez nah asmano mein chhupi hui hai nah zameen mein nah zarray se barri aur nah uss se choti, sab kuch aik numaya daftar mein darj hai"
34,4,aur yeh qayamat is liye aeye gi ke jaza day Allah unn logon ko jo imaan laaye hain aur naik amal karte rahay hain unn ke liye mughfirat hai aur rizaq kareem
34,5,"aur jin logon ne hamari ayaat ko neecha dikhaane ke liye zor lagaya hai, un ke liye bad tareen qisam ka dard naak azaab hai"
34,6,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, ilm rakhnay walay khoob jantay hain ke jo kuch tumahray rab ki taraf se tum par nazil kya gaya hai woh sara sar haq hai aur khuday-e Aziz o hammeed ka rasta dekhata hai"
34,7,"munkareen logon se kehte hain"" hum bitayen tumhe aisa shakhs jo khabar deta hai ke jab tumahray jism ka zarra zarra muntashir ho chuka ho ga is waqt tum naye suray se peda kar diye jao ge ?"
